3i to Sell Shearings Coach Company in Auction, Telegraph Says

-- B y   L a r s   P a u l s s o n
-- 
2011-04-17T09:35:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-17/3i-to-sell-shearings-coach-company-in-auction-telegraph-says.html
3i Group Plc (III)  plans to sell
Shearings Group, a U.K. company that operates coaches and resort
hotels, in an auction for about 40 million pounds ($65 million),
the Sunday Telegraph reported, without saying where it got the
information. PriceWaterhouseCoopers LLP will conduct the sale,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lars Paulsson in London at 
 lpaulsson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Stephen Voss at 
 sev@bloomberg.net  